<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Schedule Cancelled Notification</title>
</head>
<body>
  <p>Dear <%= @employee.name %>,</p>
  <p>The schedule with client <%= @client.name %> on <%= @schedule.date.strftime('%d-%m-%Y') %> has been cancelled.</p>
  <p>Please adjust your schedule accordingly.</p>
  <p>Thank you.</p>
</body>
</html>